ðŸ§ Creature Lab

Small type script project where you can biuld your own creature
out of three elements. each creature can be made of water, fire and
earth and each have their own specific attributes.

this project was built to practice core typescript concepts such as
classes, abstract classes, interfaces, enums, and basic type inheritence.

âœ¨Features:
Each creature has:
State (baby, normal, evolved)
Core element (water, fire, earth)
Attributes (attack, defend, speed)
the creature's attribute depends on it's core element.

Tech Stack:
TypeScript
Node.js
ts-node (development)

