ðŸš€Getting Started

-Clone the repository :
git clone https://github.com/your-username/creature-lab.git
cd Creature

-Install the dependencies :
npm install

-Run the project :
npx ts-node creature-lab

ðŸ’¬Example Usage
Pyro (fire) [baby] ->
attack:1  
defense:1  
speed:1

Aqua (water) [baby] ->
attack:1  
defense:1  
speed:1

Pyro evolved into a blazing form ðŸ”¥
Aqua evolved into a flowing guardian ðŸ’§

Pyro (fire) [evolved] ->
